videos.description: Zach Smith drives the lane and flushes home the two-handed slam for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith hammers home the jam

videos.description: Hayden Howell receives the bounce pass and scores on the layup for an old fashion 3-point play.
videos.headline: Abilene's Howell scores reverse layup and-1

videos.description: Zach Smith slams home the alley-oop from Keenan Evans to extend the Red Raiders' lead.
videos.headline: Smith converts tip-in dunk

videos.description: Zach Smith gets an easy dunk off the battle for a loose ball for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Mad scramble leads to Texas Tech slam

videos.description: Zhaire Smith follows up the missed shot with a thunderous two-handed jam to extend the lead.
videos.headline: Smith finishes at rim with jam

videos.description: Keenan Evans hits a soft one-handed jumper off glass and gets and-1.
videos.headline: Evans finishes old fashioned 3-point play

videos.description: B.J. Maxwell drives the baseline and scores a right-handed reverse layup for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Abilene's Maxwell finishes sweet reverse layup

videos.description: Brandone Francis swishes a 3-pointer in the right corner pocket to give the Red Raiders its largest lead of the game.
videos.headline: Tech's Francis nails corner 3-pointer
